    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135610/extras/948c70a153c0edd971a45388a4c0a350.avif?t=1756414850\" width=720 height=192 /></span>Welcome! You have chosen or been chosen to join the S.P.O.O.K. department, due to a recent influx of paranourmal activity in your region you now have to clean it out the hard way, but don't you worry, we've got you covered with everything needed for such trivial tasks, you've got your gun, a spell book and nothing else but your courrage (Additional items may be granted if you're deemed good enough), in everything else we'll assist you over the intercom to let you know what to do! (These tasks may cover cleaning out the sewers, breaking into secured locations and spinning the wheel?). We'll see you at our base!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use unusual weaponary to tear through the monsters hoarding the streets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get new and powerful spells through your runs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan out your way towards each boss</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And survive through all sorts of mayham</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly a ship into space?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135610/extras/302cb1891a6124358acc436915aff9f6.poster.avif?t=1756414850\" width=360 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135610/extras/302cb1891a6124358acc436915aff9f6.webm?t=1756414850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And remember, you don't have to fight your way through all this alone, grab your controllers with your friends (or enemies) and fight your way through together... Or fight each other... Or be ballin'</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135610/extras/01cd24004cade9d49eab7bbf9a123342.poster.avif?t=1756414850\" width=152 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135610/extras/01cd24004cade9d49eab7bbf9a123342.webm?t=1756414850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>[code]Hello? Can anyone hear me?[/code]</p>",
